Necessary packages:
1. Python3 (see: https://realpython.com/installing-python/ )
2. PyQt5
    install with 'pip3 install pyqt5'
    or with 'sudo apt-get install python3-pyqt5'
3. numpy and scipy
    install with 'python -m pip install --user numpy scipy' 
4. pyclipper
    'pip install pyclipper'


Note: pip3 should be installed with Python 3
